query:
-- Consolidate Los Angeles
UPDATE protocolChunks 
SET countyId = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name = 'Los Angeles County EMS Agency' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1)
WHERE countyId IN (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE state = 'California' AND LOWER(name) LIKE '%los angeles%' AND name != 'Los Angeles County EMS Agency');

-- Consolidate Marin
UPDATE protocolChunks 
SET countyId = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name = 'Marin County EMS' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1)
WHERE countyId IN (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE state = 'California' AND LOWER(name) LIKE '%marin%' AND name != 'Marin County EMS');

-- Consolidate Merced
UPDATE protocolChunks 
SET countyId = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name = 'Merced County EMS Agency' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1)
WHERE countyId IN (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE state = 'California' AND LOWER(name) LIKE '%merced%' AND name != 'Merced County EMS Agency');

-- Consolidate Monterey
UPDATE protocolChunks 
SET countyId = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name = 'Monterey County EMS Agency' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1)
WHERE countyId IN (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE state = 'California' AND LOWER(name) LIKE '%monterey%' AND name != 'Monterey County EMS Agency');

-- Consolidate Alpine, Amador, Calaveras, Mariposa, Tuolumne to Mountain-Valley
UPDATE protocolChunks 
SET countyId = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name = 'Mountain-Valley EMS Agency' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1)
WHERE countyId IN (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE state = 'California' AND (LOWER(name) LIKE '%alpine%' OR LOWER(name) LIKE '%amador%' OR LOWER(name) LIKE '%calaveras%' OR LOWER(name) LIKE '%mariposa%' OR LOWER(name) LIKE '%tuolumne%' OR LOWER(name) LIKE '%mountain%valley%') AND name != 'Mountain-Valley EMS Agency');

-- Consolidate Napa
UPDATE protocolChunks 
SET countyId = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name = 'Napa County EMS' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1)
WHERE countyId IN (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE state = 'California' AND LOWER(name) LIKE '%napa%' AND name != 'Napa County EMS');

-- Consolidate Del Norte, Humboldt to North Coast
UPDATE protocolChunks 
SET countyId = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name = 'North Coast EMS' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1)
WHERE countyId IN (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE state = 'California' AND (LOWER(name) LIKE '%del norte%' OR LOWER(name) LIKE '%humboldt%' OR LOWER(name) LIKE '%north coast%') AND name != 'North Coast EMS');

-- Consolidate Northern California counties
UPDATE protocolChunks 
SET countyId = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name = 'Northern California EMS Inc' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1)
WHERE countyId IN (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE state = 'California' AND (LOWER(name) LIKE '%butte%' OR LOWER(name) LIKE '%colusa%' OR LOWER(name) LIKE '%glenn%' OR LOWER(name) LIKE '%lassen%' OR LOWER(name) LIKE '%modoc%' OR LOWER(name) LIKE '%plumas%' OR LOWER(name) LIKE '%shasta%' OR LOWER(name) LIKE '%siskiyou%' OR LOWER(name) LIKE '%tehama%' OR LOWER(name) LIKE '%trinity%' OR LOWER(name) LIKE '%northern california%') AND name != 'Northern California EMS Inc');

-- Consolidate Orange
UPDATE protocolChunks 
SET countyId = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name = 'Orange County EMS Agency' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1)
WHERE countyId IN (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE state = 'California' AND LOWER(name) LIKE '%orange%' AND name != 'Orange County EMS Agency');
